<div class="col two-sm last" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn2">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Travel information</h3>
    Bus informationFrom Bradford Interchange First service 570 and 571 from stand G. From The Tyrls (Market Street) First services 640 and 641.Rail informationBradford Interchange rail station is one mile (1.5 km) away from the hospital. Bradford Forster Square rail station is 1.5 miles (2 km) approx. away. Walk to the Bradford Interchange bus station or The Tyrls for a bus connection.  


</div>
</div>
